{"tid":1831241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★三菱電機遭中國黑客組織入侵  欲偷取日本基建機密文件","createTime":"2020-01-20T08:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T11:19:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0e914d6ecae4a09a98b05a6c4487cd78dca21339","tid":1831241,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"據《朝日新聞》報導，三菱電機日前在日本以及海外超過 120 部電腦以及 40 個伺服器遭到黑客的攻擊，當中可能將會有個人資料以及公司機密因此被盜，但就強調公司內有關日本國防事務、電力以及鐵路等基建的高度機密資料並未有因此流出，呼籲人們不要擔心，並藉此向一眾受影響人士致歉。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n三菱電機就表示他們隨即在是次事件後開始進行調查工作，並發現黑客所使用的入侵方法與中國黑客組織 Tick 極為相似，再加上該組織一向以偷取不同國家的國防機密文件為目標，懷疑是次行動與他們有關。他們補充指出公司早在去年 6 月就曾經遭到同樣的攻擊，未知是否同樣由相同組織發起。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/01/20/mitsubishi-electric-was-attacked/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F01%2F20%2Fmitsubishi-electric-was-attacked%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV92hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=c7299a05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/01/20/mitsubishi-electric-was-attacked/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"4647a7fe83ab5c20b6c755da18f2456bc503b2fc","tid":1831241,"uid":86509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"春：中國人一不靠偷，二不靠搶"},{"pid":"bcf0b9e5a6a955660b20f30c59fc975611b96577","tid":1831241,"uid":224533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"支那國粹 偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"0a88d1cdbe6dcd7b25ab7d1096f96d51880e77d5","tid":1831241,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OXwS2Kv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXwS2Kv.gif&h=93b8161d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27d142423ef6d492a6b3183615c108de9ef2cb45","tid":1831241,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:55:56.000Z","msg":"要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://p